<p><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201208/6c7b705cdee44ad4b0b4da943a37720e.jpeg" width="626" height="469.5" /></p>
<p><span>△ 远眺中绒布冰川。</span></p>
<p><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201208/e25210225fd94947b71171954a7a0a5f.jpeg" width="626" height="469.5" /></p>
